reviewText: I am already the fortunate owner of two of George's workout tapes and this one does not disappoint either. I love the interval training, with short bursts of aerobics. George is his usual positive self, giving the viewer encouraging comments along the way. Petra is marvelous as she leads the viewer through a well constructed workout. For the average everyday individual such as myself, this workout is great especially when you don't have time for a full hour of exercise, but can squeeze in about half that much. It's fun and makes you feel good at the end.
Title: George Foreman: Fat Blasting Walk

reviewText: This is a good exercise tape.  It is basically a dance tape, but don't worry about being able to dance.  The moves are dance steps, but easy.  The intensity is high, by the end I felt like I had spent an hour in gym class.
Title: George Foreman: Fat Blasting Walk

reviewText: I really like this workout.  George and Petra are good together. The intervals are a good way to get your heart rate up without wearing you out.  I like the dance steps Petra does, too.  It's a nice mixture of walking, interval walking, with some rhythm.
summary: George and Petra make a nice pair
Title: George Foreman: Fat Blasting Walk

reviewText: If you are looking to break some sweat and have some fun this workout is for you.  The music is upbeat and the moves are easy to follow yet interesting and fun. The walkers are all "average people" who seem to be enjoying the workout.  George is wonderful and funny, Petra does a geat job at guiding and explaining the movements. This workout can be taylored to a variety of fitness levels.  For example, during the interval section I usually do light jogging rather than faster walk done by the walkers in the video. This is strictly a cardio workout however.  For strength training the Circuit walk or the Walk Box and Burn videos incorporate more upper body/lower body movements. This is a good fun and basic workout for beginners to moderate intensity or I use it on the lighter days in between hard workouts.
Title: George Foreman: Fat Blasting Walk

reviewText: good workout dvd, anyone looking for a workout dvd, this is it. and the price is right on foreman's workouts.
Title: George Foreman: Fat Blasting Walk
